Architecture=any
Version=0.0.28
Url=https://releases.pagure.org/xmlto/xmlto-0.0.28.tar.bz2

[Depends]
docbook-xml
docbook-xsl
libxslt

[Description]
The xmlto package is a front-end to a XSL toolchain. It chooses an appropriate
stylesheet for the conversion you want and applies it using an external XSLT
processor. It also performs any necessary post-processing.

[Install]
cd */
./configure --prefix=/usr &&
make &&
make install || exit 1
